57
00:11:13,173 --> 00:11:14,466
True, true!

58
00:11:16,218 --> 00:11:19,513
Come on! Come on!
Read, read on

59
00:11:19,680 --> 00:11:22,724
Okay, okay. "The anxiety of
the general public is very high

60
00:11:22,891 --> 00:11:26,144
because the police have not yet
completed their investigations

61
