63
00:11:37,656 --> 00:11:44,162
What is he like?
Where is he hiding?

64
00:11:44,329 --> 00:11:47,499
No one knows.
Still, he is one of us

65
00:11:47,666 --> 00:11:50,335
Is it your neighbor?

66
00:11:53,839 --> 00:11:56,508
Yes, that's right

67
00:11:57,050 --> 00:11:59,219
