68
00:11:59,386 --> 00:12:02,431
-You know very well.
-What do I know very well?

69
00:12:03,724 --> 00:12:08,395
-Think about it.
-What are you saying?

70
00:12:08,770 --> 00:12:14,526
I saw you go up those stairs
behind that little girl

71
00:12:14,693 --> 00:12:17,154
What?! You are crazy,
you dirty swine!

72
00:12:17,404 --> 00:12:20,908
Who's a swine? Me?
Or a man who chases little girls?

73
00:12:21,074 --> 00:12:23,452
You bastard! You swine!

74
00:12:23,911 --> 00:12:25,245
Murderer!

75
00:12:26,288 --> 00:12:28,373
Gentlemen! Gentlemen!

76
00:12:28,874 --> 00:12:32,169
I'll see you in court.
I'll see you in court

77
00:12:32,419 --> 00:12:35,881
Now, now, gentlemen! Calm down!

78
00:12:37,341 --> 00:12:39,176
Slanderer!

79
